column1: Creative Commons Licence by attribution (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/). Climate Change Initiative - European Space Agency, These data were produced by the University of Reading as part of the ESA CCI project. (http://surftemp.net)

Time series of 5-day sea surface_temperature averaged across ocean surface within latitudes 13.50 and 18.50 and longitudes 67.50 and 72.50, in kelvin and degree Celsius. Post-hoc corrections have been applied from Merchant and Embury (2020) https://doi.org/10.3390/rs12162554
